channel.title: An error I can't fix. [REWARD POSSIBLY]
channel.description:
Some kid gave me this tut and it gave me this error so I deleted the tut. And now I get this error. What should I do because I have no idea................. [code]:: Preparing for compile... :: Auto-setting envriomental variables... :: :: Scanning for latest JDK version... :: :: Found JDK 1.6.0_04 :: Results: client.java:95: illegal character: \127 ⌂ ^ client.java:95: ';' expected ⌂ ^ 2 errors :: Done! Press any key to continue . . .
[/code] Lol it's probably something really obvious........
